title: Bobby’s Rant On Crazy Airplane People + Amy’s Uncomfortable Situation With Her Dad's Ashes + 'Elder vs. Millennial' Returns!
itunes:title: Bobby’s Rant On Crazy Airplane People + Amy’s Uncomfortable Situation With Her Dad's Ashes + 'Elder vs. Millennial' Returns!
description:
Bobby gets very passionate about what needs to be done to these people who keep freaking out on airplanes. Amy is dealing with a really uncomfortable situation with her dad's ashes right now and wants to know how we feel about it and what we think she should do. And it’s back! Elder vs. Millennial where Eddie and Morgan2 try to answer trivia questions about each other’s generation.
